
                     A Logic Probe for the Experimenter.
                     -----------------------------------


    Minimum operating requirements are:-
    ------------------------------------

    1) Standard AMIGA A1200.
    2) Second floppy drive is needed.
    3) OCS.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

    General information:-
    ---------------------

    This tool will show a Logic ~0~, Logic ~1~, Indeterminate DC State or
    Indeterminate Pulse Train.

    This software was written using ACE basic compiler.

